WEBVTT

01:43.039 --> 01:46.030
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.130 --> 01:49.060
[Episode 7]

01:49.170 --> 01:53.780
[Outpatient]

03:05.350 --> 03:06.240
Help!

03:06.510 --> 03:07.640
Someone's following me.

03:08.420 --> 03:12.420
[Boutique de Fruits]

03:09.750 --> 03:10.370
Hurry.

03:11.840 --> 03:12.520
Don't be scared.

03:12.550 --> 03:13.390
Hide inside.

03:15.060 --> 03:18.250
[Boutique de Fruits]

03:18.870 --> 03:19.640
Uh...

03:19.750 --> 03:20.990
It's okay. Come out.

03:25.829 --> 03:26.480
Dr. Lu.

03:26.510 --> 03:27.750
What's going on?

03:32.670 --> 03:34.180
Shall we call the police?

03:34.800 --> 03:35.950
No, no need.

03:36.040 --> 03:37.200
I'm fine now.

03:38.100 --> 03:38.840
Yeah?

03:38.860 --> 03:40.510
Even if there's trouble, don't be scared.

03:40.540 --> 03:41.160
Yeah.

03:41.230 --> 03:42.290
Don't be scared.

03:42.450 --> 03:43.560
It's late at night.

03:43.600 --> 03:45.130
Don't wander around alone.

03:45.890 --> 03:46.610
Why don't

03:46.630 --> 03:47.900
we send you back?

03:47.920 --> 03:48.690
No, no.

03:48.760 --> 03:49.850
Are you really okay?

04:06.170 --> 04:07.490
Why are you here?

04:07.590 --> 04:08.670
It's so late and you weren't back,

04:08.690 --> 04:10.130
so I came out to pick you up.

04:10.710 --> 04:11.900
D-Don't you have a phone?

04:11.960 --> 04:12.870
Why didn't you call me?

04:12.910 --> 04:13.990
I was going to call you at the entrance

04:14.000 --> 04:14.750
of your hospital.

04:14.750 --> 04:15.130
Who knew

04:15.160 --> 04:16.110
you'd be back so soon?

04:16.630 --> 04:17.300
You...

04:17.709 --> 04:18.269
Why are you

04:18.310 --> 04:18.910
out of breath?

04:20.040 --> 04:21.410
Did you run back?

04:21.430 --> 04:24.000
I felt like someone was following me.

04:24.860 --> 04:25.650
Who?

04:25.860 --> 04:26.910
Where are they?

04:27.870 --> 04:29.030
I must've been mistaken.

04:29.050 --> 04:29.710
Forget it.

04:31.190 --> 04:32.030
Let's go home.

04:32.030 --> 04:32.560
Let's go.

04:36.810 --> 04:37.580
Are you okay?

04:37.750 --> 04:38.560
I'm okay.

04:38.970 --> 04:40.230
Did I bump into you?

04:40.550 --> 04:41.430
No.

04:42.220 --> 04:43.100
You scared me.

04:50.970 --> 04:51.720
Yan!

04:52.110 --> 04:52.860
Come over!

04:53.010 --> 04:53.780
Let's eat.

04:54.150 --> 04:54.550
Okay.

04:56.170 --> 04:57.080
My goodness.

04:59.280 --> 05:01.240
This looks so good!

05:01.270 --> 05:02.530
Surprised, huh?

05:02.790 --> 05:03.950
My dear Yan, thank you

05:03.950 --> 05:05.740
for letting me stay here for so long.

05:05.790 --> 05:06.110
Here.

05:06.110 --> 05:07.100
Let me take a photo.

05:07.120 --> 05:08.380
I'll send it to my mom.

05:08.950 --> 05:10.540
Praise me more to her.

05:11.150 --> 05:12.030
Gosh, you're such a

05:12.070 --> 05:12.670
great cook.

05:13.510 --> 05:14.040
Although

05:14.150 --> 05:14.990
I haven't cooked

05:15.030 --> 05:15.720
in a long time.

05:15.790 --> 05:17.280
I tried this out just now.

05:17.300 --> 05:18.610
It tastes pretty good.

05:18.870 --> 05:19.400
Let me

05:19.590 --> 05:20.440
be the judge of it.

05:20.480 --> 05:21.350
Cordyceps chicken soup.

05:21.550 --> 05:22.140
Try it!

05:22.230 --> 05:23.540
Cordyceps?

05:23.780 --> 05:25.370
Isn't it expensive?

05:26.960 --> 05:28.100
Oops.

05:28.110 --> 05:29.410
I don't mean the wild kind.

05:29.590 --> 05:31.440
It's the cheaper kind.

05:33.340 --> 05:34.350
How is it? Is it good?

05:34.390 --> 05:35.200
It's so good.

05:35.230 --> 05:35.870
It's so rich.

05:35.909 --> 05:36.900
Try the chicken.

05:37.290 --> 05:38.640
I stewed it for a long time.

05:38.780 --> 05:39.840
It's so rich.

05:42.409 --> 05:43.060
Oh, right.

05:43.360 --> 05:44.100
Um,

05:44.360 --> 05:46.590
I've checked out the apartment

05:46.750 --> 05:48.050
Wen Peng found for me.

05:48.070 --> 05:49.690
I plan to, um,

05:49.760 --> 05:51.420
move there in a few days.

05:52.420 --> 05:53.520
So soon?

05:53.900 --> 05:55.409
But I'll miss you so much.

05:57.680 --> 05:59.909
I'll miss you too.

06:01.560 --> 06:02.240
But...

06:03.270 --> 06:04.350
I can't

06:04.790 --> 06:05.930
stay here forever.

06:05.950 --> 06:06.920
That's not good.

06:06.950 --> 06:07.840
Just stay here.

06:07.950 --> 06:09.110
I don't mind.

06:09.570 --> 06:10.110
Besides,

06:10.150 --> 06:10.830
you can cook.

06:11.140 --> 06:12.140
That'll be the rent.

06:12.770 --> 06:13.800
No way.

06:14.150 --> 06:15.570
If I keep living here,

06:15.590 --> 06:17.230
you really won't be able to date.

06:17.360 --> 06:19.220
Who cares?

06:19.510 --> 06:20.510
I'm busy as an anesthesiologist.

06:20.550 --> 06:21.260
I don't have time.

06:21.370 --> 06:22.850
Hey! What are you saying?

06:23.330 --> 06:24.640
This is just an excuse.

06:24.850 --> 06:26.310
I've introduced so many people to you.

06:26.330 --> 06:27.070
But you...

06:29.510 --> 06:30.310
Yan.

06:32.210 --> 06:33.620
Be honest with me.

06:34.960 --> 06:36.350
Are you still

06:36.500 --> 06:37.400
pining over

06:37.430 --> 06:38.550
your boyfriend in uni?

06:43.250 --> 06:43.920
I knew it!

06:43.950 --> 06:44.890
It's still him, huh?

06:45.240 --> 06:45.950
Tell me.

06:45.990 --> 06:46.590
Who is it?

06:46.610 --> 06:47.210
Who is he?

06:47.240 --> 06:47.970
I am

06:48.060 --> 06:49.250
really curious.

06:49.630 --> 06:50.250
How

06:50.390 --> 06:51.370
is he like?

06:51.390 --> 06:52.420
Why are you

06:52.470 --> 06:53.159
wrapped

06:53.159 --> 06:54.230
around his finger?

06:54.690 --> 06:55.480
I'm really curious—

06:55.510 --> 06:56.590
Enough, enough.

06:56.630 --> 06:57.310
Look at you.

06:57.430 --> 06:58.560
Do you know who it is?

06:58.580 --> 06:59.480
You don't even know,

06:59.500 --> 07:00.750
yet you keep yapping.

07:00.770 --> 07:01.520
Enough already.

07:01.570 --> 07:02.770
How dare you say that?

07:02.830 --> 07:03.270
Am I even

07:03.310 --> 07:04.200
your friend?

07:04.510 --> 07:04.910
I... I...

07:04.940 --> 07:06.390
I told you everything about

07:06.430 --> 07:07.270
everyone I dated;

07:07.310 --> 07:08.470
their names and how they look.

07:08.490 --> 07:08.880
But you?

07:08.910 --> 07:10.380
I don't even know his name!

07:10.990 --> 07:11.430
I don't care.

07:11.430 --> 07:12.030
You must tell me

07:12.030 --> 07:12.390
everything today.

07:12.390 --> 07:13.230
Okay, okay.

07:14.040 --> 07:15.340
I'll tell you.

07:16.470 --> 07:17.830
But no one

07:17.870 --> 07:19.150
outside of my uni knows.

07:19.710 --> 07:20.400
I swear

07:20.430 --> 07:21.750
I will never

07:22.020 --> 07:22.910
tell anyone.

07:30.110 --> 07:30.940
Ji Chyi.

07:31.230 --> 07:32.360
What was that?

07:36.630 --> 07:37.630
Jiang Chengyi.

07:41.240 --> 07:42.120
Wait...

07:42.250 --> 07:43.210
Isn't that

07:43.360 --> 07:44.950
the super tall cop?

07:46.640 --> 07:47.870
I really never sensed

07:47.870 --> 07:49.010
anything!

07:49.120 --> 07:49.820
Wow,

07:49.840 --> 07:51.000
Matron Qiao is amazing.

07:51.020 --> 07:52.280
No wonder she's always—

07:52.420 --> 07:53.500
You guys are too gossipy.

07:53.990 --> 07:54.730
No.

07:54.760 --> 07:55.610
We talked...

07:56.430 --> 07:56.830
Wait.

07:56.909 --> 07:58.909
Then why did you two break up?

08:03.640 --> 08:04.340
Okay, okay.

08:04.950 --> 08:05.640
Forget

08:05.680 --> 08:06.790
that I asked.

08:07.340 --> 08:08.460
Let's eat.

08:10.410 --> 08:12.370
No wonder you told me

08:12.510 --> 08:14.020
he's a nice person

08:14.040 --> 08:15.320
and asked me to ask him myself.

08:15.470 --> 08:17.200
Actually, I should've realized,

08:17.250 --> 08:17.880
yeah?

08:19.400 --> 08:20.550
Eat the chicken feet.

08:20.600 --> 08:21.040
This one.

08:21.070 --> 08:21.790
You have it.

08:21.830 --> 08:22.350
It's good luck.

08:22.390 --> 08:23.030
You have it.

08:25.640 --> 08:27.040
Yan, I just have one question.

08:27.120 --> 08:28.110
Just one. Just one.

08:28.130 --> 08:29.100
J-Just one.

08:29.790 --> 08:30.640
Just one then.

08:30.670 --> 08:31.320
Shoot.

08:33.030 --> 08:33.840
Do you still like him?

08:33.870 --> 08:34.710
Does he still like you?

08:34.710 --> 08:35.630
Will you ever get back together?

08:39.530 --> 08:40.890
Was that one question?

08:40.919 --> 08:42.039
I said it in one breath,

08:42.070 --> 08:42.830
so it's one.

08:42.860 --> 08:43.789
A-Answer me, please.

08:43.809 --> 08:44.630
If you don't,

08:44.650 --> 08:45.760
it'll bother me all night.

08:45.790 --> 08:46.510
Tell me. Tell me.

08:46.510 --> 08:47.080
Fine, fine.

08:47.100 --> 08:48.090
Fine, fine.

08:50.750 --> 08:51.380
Tell me.

09:05.710 --> 09:07.130
Honestly?

09:11.830 --> 09:13.970
When I saw him again, I felt like...

09:15.800 --> 09:17.270
I haven't let him go.

09:17.290 --> 09:18.700
But if we're talking about

09:20.350 --> 09:21.790
getting back together...

09:24.830 --> 09:26.150
I think...

09:28.360 --> 09:29.910
it's impossible.

09:35.230 --> 09:36.270
Yan.

09:37.710 --> 09:39.320
I don't know

09:39.350 --> 09:40.830
what happened between you two,

09:41.270 --> 09:42.550
but...

09:42.670 --> 09:44.190
I-I won't ask anymore.

09:44.630 --> 09:45.870
I can sense that

09:46.230 --> 09:47.310
this is

09:47.380 --> 09:48.350
not a

09:48.830 --> 09:50.510
very happy memory.

09:51.750 --> 09:52.240
I...

09:56.930 --> 09:58.960
Anyway, you're always like this,

09:58.980 --> 10:00.730
hiding like an ostrich.

10:00.770 --> 10:02.280
I don't know if I should describe you

10:02.310 --> 10:02.960
that way.

10:02.990 --> 10:03.550
Anyway...

10:04.440 --> 10:06.340
Anyway, what it feels like is that

10:06.550 --> 10:09.030
you let this bad memory torture you

10:09.070 --> 10:10.430
for eight years.

10:11.200 --> 10:11.910
You...

10:12.420 --> 10:13.280
can't mention it,

10:13.330 --> 10:15.090
and you can't face it.

10:15.230 --> 10:16.030
But Yan,

10:17.070 --> 10:18.010
look at me!

10:18.700 --> 10:19.860
Listen up.

10:20.200 --> 10:22.230
When we have to deal with

10:22.260 --> 10:24.090
a wound that's suppurated

10:24.310 --> 10:25.430
and already

10:25.470 --> 10:26.430
oozing pus,

10:27.110 --> 10:28.440
we've to break it open.

10:28.670 --> 10:29.320
Then

10:29.510 --> 10:30.770
it'll heal faster.

10:31.270 --> 10:31.830
Am I right?

10:32.750 --> 10:34.160
You're even testing me?

10:34.190 --> 10:35.010
Let me ask you.

10:35.070 --> 10:36.600
What do you do after breaking it open?

10:36.620 --> 10:37.350
Are we even

10:37.390 --> 10:38.270
on the same topic?

10:39.870 --> 10:40.670
Yan.

10:42.300 --> 10:44.460
I'm being very serious.

10:44.970 --> 10:45.950
It's very easy

10:46.190 --> 10:47.840
to lose someone.

10:48.150 --> 10:49.220
But it's really hard

10:49.310 --> 10:50.300
to meet again.

10:51.270 --> 10:52.240
What you need to do

10:52.400 --> 10:54.120
is to be honest with yourself.

10:54.430 --> 10:56.220
Can you bear to lose this person

10:56.350 --> 10:57.510
whom you can't let go of

10:58.030 --> 10:59.270
again?

11:12.000 --> 11:14.300
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

11:15.700 --> 11:23.150
[Serve the People]

11:18.480 --> 11:19.250
Just now,

11:19.720 --> 11:21.010
we've located the suspect

11:21.510 --> 11:22.870
of the explosion

11:22.900 --> 11:24.430
at People's Hospital.

11:24.780 --> 11:25.830
Jiang Chengyi will be

11:26.260 --> 11:27.470
in charge of this arrest.

11:27.590 --> 11:28.050
Yes.

11:28.970 --> 11:30.350
The suspect

11:30.610 --> 11:32.120
is in a residential area.

11:32.430 --> 11:33.420
It's very crowded.

11:33.710 --> 11:34.610
He might have

11:34.640 --> 11:35.950
more dangerous explosives on him.

11:36.160 --> 11:37.400
So for this operation,

11:37.620 --> 11:38.930
try to refrain from using guns.

11:39.190 --> 11:39.940
Got it?

11:40.000 --> 11:40.970
-Yes.
-Yes.

11:41.410 --> 11:41.870
Okay.

11:42.070 --> 11:43.140
Get ready now.

11:52.360 --> 11:53.560
Keep an eye on the exit.

11:54.020 --> 11:54.470
Go up.

11:54.500 --> 11:54.950
Let's go.

12:51.650 --> 12:52.690
Who is it?

12:55.790 --> 12:56.470
Who is it?

12:56.710 --> 12:57.750
Hello, madam.

12:57.790 --> 12:58.590
I'm from the unit below.

12:58.630 --> 12:59.720
My apartment is leaking.

12:59.750 --> 13:00.590
I want to check

13:00.590 --> 13:01.670
if it's from your unit.

13:07.270 --> 13:07.950
Thank you.

13:07.950 --> 13:09.050
Sorry for the trouble.

13:11.280 --> 13:12.440
Don't open the door!

13:13.720 --> 13:14.560
What are you doing?

13:14.600 --> 13:15.070
Police.

13:15.110 --> 13:16.070
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

13:33.740 --> 13:34.310
I...

13:36.580 --> 13:37.180
I...

13:56.660 --> 13:57.360
Down there.

14:02.870 --> 14:03.590
-Freeze!
-Freeze!

14:05.400 --> 14:06.150
My leg.

14:08.240 --> 14:08.790
My leg!

14:14.540 --> 14:15.190
How is it?

14:15.230 --> 14:15.600
Captain Jiang.

14:15.630 --> 14:16.540
There’s no weapon.

14:19.510 --> 14:20.600
Send him to the hospital.

14:22.290 --> 14:23.060
Help him up.

14:25.500 --> 14:28.090
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

14:37.670 --> 14:38.510
This person...

14:40.070 --> 14:40.670
Here.

14:50.220 --> 14:50.990
Captain Jiang.

14:51.010 --> 14:52.310
How did the patient get hurt?

14:52.330 --> 14:54.080
He fell from a height.

14:54.100 --> 14:55.110
Blood pressure is 140,

14:55.130 --> 14:56.030
100.

14:56.240 --> 14:57.150
Heart rate is 100.

14:57.580 --> 14:58.390
His head and neck

14:58.410 --> 14:59.810
are likely to be injured.

14:59.840 --> 15:01.450
His left arm and left leg are deformed.

15:01.550 --> 15:03.070
The patient is in a coma.

15:03.100 --> 15:04.490
He needs intubation immediately.

15:04.510 --> 15:05.510
Inform Radiology

15:05.530 --> 15:06.740
to do a CT scan now.

15:13.540 --> 15:14.460
Dr. Lu.

15:14.960 --> 15:15.800
Sorry for the trouble.

15:21.460 --> 15:22.260
Let me do it.

15:23.520 --> 15:24.480
You stay here.

15:26.800 --> 15:28.150
Don't forget that the patient

15:28.150 --> 15:28.840
who was just sent here

15:28.870 --> 15:30.170
must abstain from food and water for three hours.

15:29.680 --> 15:35.700
[Department of Anesthesiology]

15:30.440 --> 15:31.820
Pay attention to his blood pressure.

15:31.870 --> 15:32.960
Be on high alert.

15:33.070 --> 15:33.360
Okay.

15:33.360 --> 15:33.890
Matron Qiao.

15:35.150 --> 15:35.910
Do you have a minute?

15:36.280 --> 15:36.870
What is it?

15:37.460 --> 15:38.000
About

15:38.000 --> 15:39.590
the patient we sent over,

15:39.750 --> 15:40.650
do you know him?

15:41.810 --> 15:42.990
He seemed familiar.

15:43.030 --> 15:43.710
But...

15:44.170 --> 15:45.190
I can't remember.

15:45.820 --> 15:47.200
Let me show you a photo.

15:47.960 --> 15:49.440
His name is Liu Yuming.

15:50.390 --> 15:52.090
Here's a photo. See if it jogs your memory.

15:53.450 --> 15:54.670
Liu Yuming?

15:58.240 --> 15:59.600
I remember now.

16:00.030 --> 16:01.260
It was last year, I think.

16:01.670 --> 16:03.470
His mom brought him here to see a doctor.

16:03.990 --> 16:05.240
He was diagnosed with

16:05.260 --> 16:07.500
mid-to-late stage schizophrenia.

16:08.190 --> 16:09.480
All our doctors examined him

16:09.520 --> 16:10.800
and came up with a treatment plan.

16:11.120 --> 16:13.180
But he couldn't be cured,

16:13.330 --> 16:14.520
so he was discharged.

16:14.560 --> 16:15.240
Discharged?

16:15.610 --> 16:16.460
And?

16:16.950 --> 16:19.320
Then they came again many times.

16:19.350 --> 16:21.280
His mom told all the doctors

16:21.310 --> 16:22.560
that he excelled in school

16:22.590 --> 16:23.830
and has a PhD.

16:23.910 --> 16:25.250
We sympathized with him,

16:25.310 --> 16:26.310
but this illness

16:26.310 --> 16:27.150
is hard to cure.

16:27.150 --> 16:28.600
We had no other choice.

16:28.720 --> 16:29.970
He even has a PhD?

16:30.410 --> 16:31.280
Do you have his info?

16:32.850 --> 16:34.620
I'll get his medical records for you.

16:34.650 --> 16:34.990
Okay.

16:35.480 --> 16:36.300
Give me a moment.

16:40.580 --> 16:43.490
[Emergency]

16:57.040 --> 16:58.670
Liu, you'll have to take on the first midnight shift.

16:59.120 --> 16:59.630
Yes.

17:04.270 --> 17:05.270
He's still unconscious.

17:05.290 --> 17:06.260
You can interrogate him

17:06.290 --> 17:07.220
when he wakes up.

17:08.240 --> 17:08.750
Okay.

17:08.790 --> 17:09.480
Sorry for the trouble,

17:09.510 --> 17:09.910
Dr. Lu.

17:10.470 --> 17:11.280
It's no problem.

17:11.680 --> 17:12.500
Is any of you...

17:15.010 --> 17:16.170
hurt or anything?

17:16.740 --> 17:17.680
Did you get checked up?

17:18.369 --> 17:19.400
W-We're all fine.

17:19.420 --> 17:20.160
Right?

17:20.190 --> 17:20.829
Yes.

17:21.210 --> 17:21.880
We're all fine.

17:22.400 --> 17:23.079
Captain Jiang.

17:23.099 --> 17:23.750
Um,

17:23.770 --> 17:24.710
it's your first day at work.

17:24.740 --> 17:25.430
You must be tired.

17:25.579 --> 17:26.800
Why don't you go home?

17:26.819 --> 17:28.400
The two of us will stay here.

17:28.450 --> 17:29.330
What's wrong with you?

17:29.360 --> 17:29.780
Get lost.

17:29.780 --> 17:30.390
What's wrong with you?

17:30.410 --> 17:30.880
No, I...

17:30.900 --> 17:31.660
Get lost!

17:32.140 --> 17:32.830
Jiang.

17:33.080 --> 17:34.490
You had a tough day,

17:34.520 --> 17:35.110
but at night,

17:35.130 --> 17:36.560
please keep working hard with us

17:36.590 --> 17:37.740
for night duty.

17:38.520 --> 17:39.780
Alright, cut the crap.

17:41.320 --> 17:42.560
I'll keep watch.

17:42.590 --> 17:43.490
Go eat something.

17:43.510 --> 17:44.580
Wait, Captain Jiang,

17:44.750 --> 17:45.770
is it appropriate?

17:46.450 --> 17:47.150
Wait.

17:47.620 --> 17:49.070
We'll take over after eating.

17:50.030 --> 17:51.830
It's Captain Jiang's first day.

17:54.060 --> 17:55.260
Are you on night duty too?

17:59.710 --> 18:00.550
You...

18:01.800 --> 18:03.310
H-Have you eaten?

18:04.020 --> 18:05.400
No, but

18:05.430 --> 18:06.550
I'm no longer hungry.

18:09.050 --> 18:09.690
Then...

18:10.100 --> 18:11.740
You should get some rest.

18:11.870 --> 18:12.510
The medical staff are here.

18:12.570 --> 18:13.500
Don't worry.

18:13.530 --> 18:14.750
I'll check on other patients.

18:14.780 --> 18:15.590
Go ahead.

18:45.600 --> 18:46.960
♫As the city flickers♫

18:48.300 --> 18:51.080
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

18:52.360 --> 18:53.660
♫And you, who loves to smile♫

18:54.110 --> 18:54.600
Jiang.

18:54.150 --> 18:56.630
[Emergency]

18:54.630 --> 18:55.610
We're here to take over.

18:54.670 --> 18:57.130
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

18:55.960 --> 18:56.910
Get some sleep.

18:58.160 --> 19:00.500
♫The humor of time♫

19:01.990 --> 19:04.440
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

19:05.510 --> 19:11.260
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

19:12.650 --> 19:14.270
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

19:15.380 --> 19:18.230
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

19:19.530 --> 19:20.950
♫The stubborn me♫

19:22.180 --> 19:24.880
♫I always think of the far future♫

19:25.670 --> 19:27.740
♫I walk willfully♫

19:29.110 --> 19:32.030
♫Like a star revolving around♫

19:32.670 --> 19:33.980
♫I turn around♫

19:35.150 --> 19:38.650
♫But you're not behind me♫

19:40.320 --> 19:41.900
♫Losing you♫

19:42.720 --> 19:44.890
♫It's so unreal♫

19:46.090 --> 19:47.520
♫I hurt my love♫

19:48.230 --> 19:49.180
♫But still hope to♫

19:49.920 --> 19:52.620
♫Start anew♫

19:53.820 --> 19:55.830
♫There’s a certain kind of squander♫

19:56.780 --> 19:58.910
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

20:00.460 --> 20:02.440
♫When you're not here♫

20:03.240 --> 20:06.540
♫Life becomes aimless♫

20:07.400 --> 20:09.080
♫I miss you♫

20:10.170 --> 20:12.310
♫It's so real♫

20:13.400 --> 20:14.940
♫The person I trust♫

20:15.520 --> 20:16.620
♫Insists on separating♫

20:17.140 --> 20:20.070
♫Who can explain?♫

20:21.290 --> 20:23.220
♫I'm not afraid of your happiness♫

20:24.270 --> 20:26.470
♫I'm afraid you'll forget me♫

20:27.300 --> 20:29.740
♫To feel my heartache♫

20:30.710 --> 20:32.290
♫When I no longer have the best♫

20:31.050 --> 20:32.760
He won't wake up tonight.

20:33.340 --> 20:36.890
♫I miss you missing me♫

20:33.400 --> 20:34.830
You should get some sleep.

21:13.990 --> 21:14.810
Coming.

21:15.540 --> 21:17.200
So Liu Yuming

21:17.230 --> 21:19.330
was so obsessed with explosives engineering

21:19.350 --> 21:20.950
that he developed schizophrenia

21:20.980 --> 21:22.350
and became paranoid.

21:22.450 --> 21:24.090
After he hit the victim with his car,

21:24.110 --> 21:25.670
he tied a bomb to him.

21:26.280 --> 21:27.190
In my opinion,

21:27.230 --> 21:29.040
Captain Jiang's really awesome.

21:29.240 --> 21:30.360
Decisive and efficient—

21:30.470 --> 21:31.550
Cut the crap.

21:31.570 --> 21:32.150
Excuse me,

21:32.190 --> 21:32.790
are those our noodles?

21:32.830 --> 21:33.310
Coming.

21:33.310 --> 21:33.680
Hurry.

21:33.710 --> 21:34.240
Stuff his mouth.

21:34.270 --> 21:35.150
Coming.

21:35.870 --> 21:36.430
Director Xing first.

21:36.450 --> 21:37.010
Here.

21:37.040 --> 21:37.560
Okay.

21:37.600 --> 21:38.320
Careful, it’s hot.

21:39.630 --> 21:40.490
Jiang,

21:40.590 --> 21:41.240
not bad.

21:41.320 --> 21:42.050
It's your

21:42.080 --> 21:42.600
first case here

21:42.620 --> 21:43.870
and you already aced it.

21:45.120 --> 21:47.020
You've brought good luck to Anshan's

21:47.210 --> 21:48.510
Criminal Investigation Unit.

21:48.550 --> 21:49.210
Director.

21:49.240 --> 21:50.480
It's all thanks to everyone.

21:50.510 --> 21:51.900
I didn't do it alone.

21:52.390 --> 21:53.080
Yue.

21:53.100 --> 21:54.190
Speak up for us.

21:55.590 --> 21:56.130
Director Xing,

21:56.160 --> 21:57.290
it was a team effort.

21:57.670 --> 21:59.020
We also need commendation.

21:59.060 --> 21:59.820
We also need praise.

21:59.840 --> 22:00.640
Yes, that's right.

22:00.730 --> 22:02.040
We played a part too.

22:02.060 --> 22:03.130
Fine, fine.

22:03.350 --> 22:04.530
All of you,

22:04.550 --> 22:05.210
well done!

22:05.390 --> 22:06.030
Everyone

22:06.070 --> 22:07.450
did superb this time.

22:07.470 --> 22:08.120
As usual,

22:08.750 --> 22:10.020
let's have a gathering sometime.

22:10.270 --> 22:10.830
Barbecue,

22:10.990 --> 22:11.620
my treat.

22:11.740 --> 22:12.340
-Okay?
-Nice.

22:12.370 --> 22:12.960
Nice.

22:12.990 --> 22:13.430
Nice.

22:13.430 --> 22:14.090
Director Xing.

22:14.710 --> 22:15.470
Can we bring

22:15.490 --> 22:16.500
our family?

22:16.530 --> 22:17.280
Sure.

22:17.520 --> 22:19.370
But only one family member each.

22:19.390 --> 22:20.280
That's enough.

22:21.060 --> 22:21.830
Captain Jiang

22:21.870 --> 22:23.030
only has Dr. Lu anyway.

22:23.880 --> 22:24.750
Dr. Lu?

22:26.280 --> 22:27.480
Dr. Lu?

22:29.570 --> 22:30.200
Jiang,

22:30.230 --> 22:31.070
what’s going on?

22:31.080 --> 22:32.510
Is Lu your girlfriend?

22:32.960 --> 22:33.590
No.

22:34.280 --> 22:35.320
No,

22:35.430 --> 22:36.330
it's more than that.

22:36.350 --> 22:37.970
Sooner or later, she'll be his girl.

22:38.600 --> 22:39.590
You...

22:41.060 --> 22:42.130
Wait, Yue,

22:42.410 --> 22:44.070
I'm a bit confused.

22:44.090 --> 22:45.640
More than a girlfriend?

22:45.700 --> 22:46.590
So are they

22:46.610 --> 22:47.730
a thing or not?

22:47.760 --> 22:48.940
Care to explain, Captain Jiang?

22:49.030 --> 22:50.480
It doesn’t matter.

22:50.840 --> 22:51.610
Anyway,

22:51.640 --> 22:53.030
every time Captain Jiang

22:53.060 --> 22:54.340
returns from seeing Dr. Lu,

22:54.390 --> 22:56.130
he becomes very gentle in the way

22:56.160 --> 22:57.500
he speaks and acts.

22:57.520 --> 22:58.990
Back in the police academy,

22:59.030 --> 23:00.310
he was so fierce to me, you know?

23:00.330 --> 23:02.270
Shut your mouth with this.

23:02.910 --> 23:04.070
Have some spicy food

23:04.330 --> 23:06.050
to tame the gossip in your mouth.

23:06.070 --> 23:07.210
Sure thing.

23:07.650 --> 23:09.170
We're a family, aren't we?

23:09.200 --> 23:10.390
Director Xing's here too.

23:10.920 --> 23:12.210
Just be honest with us.

23:12.230 --> 23:12.750
Come on.

23:12.770 --> 23:13.960
Yes, Jiang.

23:14.790 --> 23:15.870
Tell us.

23:16.610 --> 23:18.170
I'm also quite curious.

23:21.360 --> 23:22.410
Well...

23:23.070 --> 23:24.990
Dr. Lu and I...

23:27.220 --> 23:29.380
when we were in university,

23:30.620 --> 23:31.630
we were classmates.

23:32.590 --> 23:33.330
Classmates.

23:33.590 --> 23:34.250
And then?

23:35.460 --> 23:36.750
That's all. Just classmates.

23:39.020 --> 23:39.720
Let's eat.

23:39.750 --> 23:40.400
Alright, eat up.

23:40.430 --> 23:40.950
Eat up.

23:51.630 --> 23:52.370
So spicy!

23:52.800 --> 23:53.650
Is it?

23:55.870 --> 23:56.580
Have some soup.

23:58.820 --> 24:00.330
How do you feel back at work?

24:00.440 --> 24:01.920
It's been bad.

24:01.960 --> 24:02.640
I can't handle it.

24:02.670 --> 24:04.240
It's so overwhelming.

24:04.750 --> 24:05.710
You haven't used up your annual leave.

24:05.730 --> 24:07.280
Take a few more days off.

24:08.030 --> 24:09.170
I can't.

24:09.190 --> 24:10.860
The nurses' station is so swamped.

24:10.880 --> 24:12.750
If it weren't for the matter with Zhang Xiaohui,

24:12.780 --> 24:13.780
Matron Qiao

24:13.800 --> 24:15.500
would've cursed me out.

24:16.010 --> 24:17.070
Did Zhang Xiaohui

24:17.110 --> 24:18.230
really get arrested?

24:22.310 --> 24:24.240
Did I not tell you?

24:24.600 --> 24:25.590
Actually,

24:25.610 --> 24:27.130
his ex-girlfriend didn't cheat.

24:27.680 --> 24:29.230
It was also because he was

24:29.300 --> 24:29.870
too controlling

24:29.890 --> 24:30.970
that they broke up.

24:32.030 --> 24:33.450
And he even

24:33.550 --> 24:35.590
stalked her for half a year.

24:36.540 --> 24:37.490
And now,

24:37.530 --> 24:38.370
he's locked up.

24:38.510 --> 24:39.270
Serves him right.

24:41.010 --> 24:42.540
Sorry about that.

24:42.580 --> 24:44.090
I'll give you a huge drumstick.

24:44.120 --> 24:45.280
You have it.

24:45.330 --> 24:46.810
Your surgeries are so taxing.

24:46.830 --> 24:47.770
You need the energy.

24:47.870 --> 24:48.870
Eat more.

24:49.100 --> 24:49.660
Okay, okay.

24:49.680 --> 24:50.470
Lu Yan.

24:51.080 --> 24:52.180
Captain Jiang, why are you...

24:53.250 --> 24:54.890
You must be here for Yan.

24:55.340 --> 24:56.880
How's your case going?

24:57.850 --> 24:58.630
Pretty good.

24:58.650 --> 24:59.630
I just ate noodles.

24:59.780 --> 25:00.550
They were good,

25:00.570 --> 25:01.640
so I brought you some.

25:01.670 --> 25:02.380
Try it.

25:03.160 --> 25:05.030
Captain Jiang, you're so nice.

25:06.010 --> 25:06.690
Here.

25:07.250 --> 25:08.080
Thank you.

25:09.590 --> 25:10.340
You too.

25:10.420 --> 25:11.040
Yes.

25:11.060 --> 25:11.970
Thank you.

25:14.470 --> 25:15.540
And intestines too?

25:21.470 --> 25:22.020
Oh, right.

25:22.050 --> 25:23.250
Captain Jiang.

25:23.280 --> 25:24.920
Are you free tonight?

25:25.040 --> 25:25.920
What's up?

25:26.530 --> 25:28.250
I just moved to a new place.

25:28.270 --> 25:29.490
I want to invite

25:29.570 --> 25:31.340
everyone to dinner tonight.

25:31.940 --> 25:32.760
Yan's coming too.

25:32.800 --> 25:33.900
Care to join?

25:37.710 --> 25:38.540
I may have

25:38.570 --> 25:39.640
work to do.

25:39.660 --> 25:40.790
I'll check first, okay?

25:41.070 --> 25:43.010
They're all people you know,

25:43.280 --> 25:44.640
like Matron Qiao,

25:44.670 --> 25:45.660
Dr. Huang,

25:45.750 --> 25:46.630
Yilin,

25:46.790 --> 25:47.620
and...

25:48.160 --> 25:49.780
Tang Jie and her husband.

25:49.800 --> 25:50.880
You know them too.

25:51.890 --> 25:53.180
How do you know them?

25:53.210 --> 25:55.060
I needed to fix my teeth.

25:55.100 --> 25:55.670
So Yan

25:55.720 --> 25:57.100
gave me her contact.

25:57.140 --> 25:57.950
Tang Jie

25:57.990 --> 25:58.940
is really nice.

25:59.080 --> 26:00.310
I haven't had the chance to thank her.

26:00.350 --> 26:01.130
So I thought

26:01.150 --> 26:02.530
I'll do it together this time.

26:03.080 --> 26:04.040
I also heard

26:04.080 --> 26:05.200
her husband

26:05.230 --> 26:07.330
runs a film company.

26:07.350 --> 26:08.780
So I thought

26:08.800 --> 26:10.010
he could introduce

26:10.040 --> 26:11.330
some hotties to me.

26:11.720 --> 26:13.360
Still boy-crazy?

26:17.060 --> 26:18.250
How is it? Is it good?

26:18.280 --> 26:18.840
Yeah.

26:19.630 --> 26:20.740
H-Have you had your fill?

26:20.760 --> 26:22.090
Yes, I have.

26:25.140 --> 26:25.990
By the way,

26:26.490 --> 26:27.660
Wen Peng's coming too.

26:27.680 --> 26:28.890
You know him too.

26:30.300 --> 26:31.600
You know Wen Peng too?

26:31.890 --> 26:33.070
Yes, he's my senior.

26:33.390 --> 26:34.570
And he found

26:34.600 --> 26:36.060
my apartment for me.

26:37.760 --> 26:40.210
You guys hung out with him often?

26:40.310 --> 26:41.030
Yes.

26:41.640 --> 26:42.950
Well, since they're

26:42.980 --> 26:44.070
all people you know,

26:44.090 --> 26:45.040
you should join us.

26:46.330 --> 26:47.880
Okay, I'll check my workload.

26:48.040 --> 26:49.950
If I get off work early,

26:49.990 --> 26:50.870
I'll try my best to make it.

26:51.040 --> 26:51.590
Okay.

26:51.650 --> 26:52.680
If you're coming,

26:52.680 --> 26:53.950
contact Yan.

26:53.970 --> 26:54.610
Okay.

27:18.200 --> 27:19.440
We're not done yet!

27:19.510 --> 27:20.370
You...

27:21.480 --> 27:21.950
Wait,

27:21.950 --> 27:22.950
what about selfies?

27:22.970 --> 27:23.870
Just food photos?

27:23.910 --> 27:24.400
Right.

27:24.400 --> 27:24.830
Yes, yes.

27:24.850 --> 27:25.590
Let's take a group photo.

27:25.630 --> 27:25.990
Let me.

27:26.030 --> 27:27.040
This angle's good.

27:28.380 --> 27:28.950
Thank you.

27:28.950 --> 27:30.430
Women love taking photos.

27:30.470 --> 27:31.070
Make sure we're all

27:31.090 --> 27:31.880
in the frame.

27:32.440 --> 27:33.740
Matron Qiao, squeeze in more.

27:34.120 --> 27:34.680
Okay.

27:35.830 --> 27:37.910
Three, two, one.

27:37.930 --> 27:38.950
Cheese!

27:38.990 --> 27:39.830
Cheese!

27:40.680 --> 27:41.340
Cheers.

27:42.630 --> 27:43.770
Let me see.

27:44.350 --> 27:44.910
Let me check.

27:44.930 --> 27:45.570
Let me see.

27:46.950 --> 27:48.300
This part's all blurred.

27:48.320 --> 27:48.890
Yeah.

27:48.920 --> 27:49.710
Send it to the group chat.

27:49.740 --> 27:50.810
-Send it to the group chat.
-We can edit it.

27:50.840 --> 27:51.600
It can be edited.

27:52.010 --> 27:52.750
Director Sun,

27:53.160 --> 27:54.720
why isn't your husband here?

27:55.640 --> 27:57.400
He has an operation tonight.

27:57.640 --> 27:59.030
He works at a large hospital.

27:59.060 --> 28:00.110
It's not as idle as

28:00.150 --> 28:01.070
our district hospital.

28:01.100 --> 28:02.110
To be honest,

28:02.150 --> 28:03.570
we haven't seen each other for a long time.

28:03.590 --> 28:04.030
Thank god

28:04.070 --> 28:05.420
my parents are watching our kid.

28:06.060 --> 28:06.880
That's why

28:06.910 --> 28:08.290
doctors shouldn't get married.

28:08.330 --> 28:09.120
That's right.

28:09.290 --> 28:10.370
Really?

28:10.550 --> 28:12.070
I think it's quite nice.

28:12.470 --> 28:13.210
And you'll

28:13.240 --> 28:14.570
understand each other better.

28:16.030 --> 28:18.080
But don't you think doctors

28:18.290 --> 28:19.180
are a good match

28:19.370 --> 28:20.380
with cops?

28:21.400 --> 28:22.280
Right?

28:22.310 --> 28:23.810
Aren't you talking about Yan

28:23.830 --> 28:24.960
and Captain Jiang?

28:24.990 --> 28:26.620
Qianqian, you're so smart!

28:26.650 --> 28:28.440
I think they're a good match too.

28:28.450 --> 28:29.650
But to be honest,

28:29.680 --> 28:31.030
if they got married,

28:31.190 --> 28:32.740
they won't be able to see each other.

28:33.170 --> 28:33.900
Why?

28:33.950 --> 28:34.710
No.

28:34.740 --> 28:36.260
It's fine as long as their hearts are one.

28:36.290 --> 28:37.060
That's right.

28:38.110 --> 28:39.300
A loving relationship.

28:39.740 --> 28:40.580
Who

28:40.950 --> 28:42.040
wants drinks?

28:43.190 --> 28:44.200
Coke Zero.

28:44.840 --> 28:45.930
-Me, me!
-Yes, yes!

28:45.960 --> 28:46.630
You?

28:46.850 --> 28:47.650
No, thanks.

28:47.670 --> 28:48.900
Don't drink too much soda.

28:49.070 --> 28:49.510
Thank you.

28:49.540 --> 28:50.060
Thank you!

28:50.090 --> 28:50.910
It's bad for you.

28:50.930 --> 28:52.330
Wen, you're so sweet.

28:58.910 --> 28:59.710
Lu Yan!

29:03.380 --> 29:05.450
W-Weren't you not coming?

29:05.610 --> 29:06.270
Yes.

29:06.290 --> 29:07.330
Let me help you.

29:07.620 --> 29:09.600
I happened to be done with my work

29:09.620 --> 29:10.300
and...

29:10.640 --> 29:11.800
It's a rare gathering.

29:11.830 --> 29:13.190
The more, the merrier.

29:15.910 --> 29:16.480
Let's go.

29:16.500 --> 29:17.030
Let's go.

29:19.120 --> 29:19.800
Lu Yan!

29:22.130 --> 29:22.840
Wen.

29:23.940 --> 29:25.130
Everyone's waiting for you.

29:25.840 --> 29:26.700
We meet again.

29:27.420 --> 29:28.770
I didn't expect you to come.

29:29.370 --> 29:30.700
I was invited.

29:30.980 --> 29:31.700
Let's go.

29:32.580 --> 29:32.990
Let's go.

29:33.030 --> 29:34.060
I'm starving.

29:41.190 --> 29:42.260
Qianqian.

29:42.390 --> 29:43.100
Qianqian.

29:43.150 --> 29:43.590
They're here.

29:43.670 --> 29:44.590
Yan, you're here!

29:44.710 --> 29:45.270
Jiang, why are you here?

29:45.270 --> 29:46.210
Captain Jiang, you're here too!

29:46.310 --> 29:47.510
Lu Yan and I bought you gifts.

29:47.510 --> 29:48.350
Oh my god, thank you.

29:49.150 --> 29:50.230
Why's Captain Jiang

29:50.270 --> 29:51.110
carrying

29:51.130 --> 29:52.680
Dr. Lu's stuff?

29:53.230 --> 29:54.470
I just helped her.

29:54.690 --> 29:55.460
Lu Yan.

29:55.560 --> 29:56.680
I saved this seat for you.

29:57.350 --> 29:57.970
Then...

29:58.080 --> 29:58.630
It's okay.

29:58.680 --> 29:59.550
I'll get another chair.

30:00.170 --> 30:00.880
Here.

30:00.900 --> 30:01.510
Okay.

30:01.630 --> 30:02.480
Sit here.

30:03.070 --> 30:03.760
Lu Yan.

30:03.810 --> 30:05.650
Want to sit next to your bestie?

30:06.220 --> 30:06.980
Sure.

30:07.010 --> 30:07.430
Here.

30:07.430 --> 30:08.090
Yan, sit here.

30:08.760 --> 30:09.510
Is it cramped?

30:09.550 --> 30:09.920
Sit.

30:09.950 --> 30:10.580
I...

30:10.610 --> 30:11.320
It's okay.

30:15.410 --> 30:16.520
Is it cramped there?

30:17.680 --> 30:18.660
I-It's okay.

30:18.980 --> 30:20.210
I'll make space for her.

30:20.230 --> 30:21.120
I'll move this way.

30:21.190 --> 30:21.940
Okay.

30:23.650 --> 30:24.910
Is it good now?

30:28.390 --> 30:29.170
Yes.

30:30.620 --> 30:32.010
Alright, everyone's here.

30:32.030 --> 30:33.070
Fill your glasses.

30:33.090 --> 30:33.750
I will

30:33.790 --> 30:35.230
give a speech soon!

30:35.270 --> 30:36.660
-Come on!
-Come on!

30:38.770 --> 30:39.340
Lu Yan.

30:39.450 --> 30:40.300
Do you want some?

30:40.320 --> 30:41.430
I don't drink anymore.

30:41.450 --> 30:42.710
It's a celebration.

30:43.300 --> 30:44.460
She can't drink.

30:44.490 --> 30:45.450
Doctors are

30:45.480 --> 30:46.240
like cops.

30:46.260 --> 30:47.380
We shouldn't drink casually.

30:47.490 --> 30:48.190
Right?

30:48.500 --> 30:49.070
Orange juice?

30:49.090 --> 30:49.720
Okay.

30:49.750 --> 30:50.360
Here.

30:50.400 --> 30:51.030
Okay.

30:51.110 --> 30:52.270
Pour some for me.

30:52.290 --> 30:53.150
I'll drink with you.

30:53.180 --> 30:53.860
Come on.

30:54.070 --> 30:55.670
You're drunk. Stop drinking.

30:55.700 --> 30:57.460
I'm having fun. I'll take tomorrow off.

30:57.530 --> 30:58.400
Fill it up!

30:59.250 --> 30:59.820
Here.

30:59.860 --> 31:00.780
Dr. Lu.

31:00.800 --> 31:02.170
Are you

31:02.200 --> 31:03.860
and Captain Jiang...

31:04.440 --> 31:05.340
We...

31:05.420 --> 31:07.830
We were university classmates.

31:09.520 --> 31:11.050
Uni classmates?

31:13.270 --> 31:14.550
Classmates...

31:17.620 --> 31:19.510
Did you two come together

31:19.830 --> 31:20.660
or...

31:20.770 --> 31:22.180
I ran into her at the door.

31:22.430 --> 31:23.570
Coincidentally?

31:24.070 --> 31:24.550
Yeah.

31:24.570 --> 31:25.410
It must be fate.

31:26.410 --> 31:28.680
-So fated.
-So fated.

31:28.700 --> 31:29.780
Not only that.

31:29.800 --> 31:31.030
They were dating

31:31.110 --> 31:31.790
in university—

31:31.810 --> 31:32.400
Honey!

31:32.550 --> 31:33.710
What's wrong with you?

31:34.260 --> 31:35.360
Why's he so drunk?

31:35.390 --> 31:36.150
What's wrong?

31:37.210 --> 31:37.740
Qianqian!

31:37.770 --> 31:39.360
Your speech. We all have our drinks.

31:41.530 --> 31:42.900
Thank you for gracing the occasion

31:42.930 --> 31:43.950
with your presence.

31:43.990 --> 31:45.420
I'm truly honored.

31:45.460 --> 31:45.890
Come on!

31:45.910 --> 31:47.210
Cheers to everyone!

31:47.240 --> 31:47.680
Here.

31:47.710 --> 31:48.460
Congrats.

31:48.490 --> 31:49.740
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

31:49.770 --> 31:50.850
Thank you!

31:50.950 --> 31:52.110
-Together.
-Congrats.

31:52.110 --> 31:53.440
Enjoy the food and drinks. Don't waste it.

31:55.190 --> 31:56.630
My second toast

31:56.650 --> 31:58.030
is to thank Lu Yan.

31:58.370 --> 31:59.590
My dear Yan, thank you

31:59.590 --> 32:00.830
for taking care of me

32:00.850 --> 32:01.640
and protecting me

32:01.660 --> 32:02.480
all this time,

32:02.500 --> 32:03.500
and even taking me in.

32:03.960 --> 32:05.720
I'm willing to exchange all my fat

32:05.750 --> 32:08.610
for endless luck in love for you!

32:09.230 --> 32:10.460
Is Lu Yan dating someone?

32:12.110 --> 32:13.310
Who is it?

32:19.630 --> 32:21.510
He's right under our noses.

32:22.450 --> 32:23.430
You two made up?

32:23.450 --> 32:24.270
My goodness.

32:24.290 --> 32:25.620
Can you just shut up?

32:26.080 --> 32:27.150
He's drunk.

32:28.400 --> 32:30.180
Don't listen to Zhong.

32:30.360 --> 32:31.490
I-I-It's...

32:31.730 --> 32:32.830
Say something.

32:32.860 --> 32:33.590
I...

32:33.700 --> 32:34.540
Right.

32:34.570 --> 32:35.650
No more drinking.

32:35.900 --> 32:37.110
We were uni classmates.

32:37.150 --> 32:39.600
In university, we were...

32:40.160 --> 32:42.030
often together...

32:42.160 --> 32:43.490
Together?

32:45.620 --> 32:46.400
Running.

32:46.910 --> 32:48.630
Is that so, Yan?

32:49.200 --> 32:50.560
Yes, running.

32:51.260 --> 32:51.780
Yes.

33:05.290 --> 33:06.310
Look at how our junior

33:06.310 --> 33:07.150
Lu Yan's running.

33:07.180 --> 33:08.370
She's like a zombie.

33:09.490 --> 33:10.480
It must've been hard on her

33:10.510 --> 33:11.510
to catch the thief.

33:12.790 --> 33:13.800
You know her?

33:14.740 --> 33:16.130
Not really.

33:16.160 --> 33:16.940
Do you know

33:16.960 --> 33:17.980
she's a cheerleader?

33:18.190 --> 33:18.990
I saw her cheerleading

33:19.010 --> 33:20.070
by chance.

33:20.140 --> 33:21.790
Zero coordination.

33:22.630 --> 33:24.810
She has such poor motor skills.

33:24.840 --> 33:26.610
Is there something wrong with her brain?

33:27.550 --> 33:28.720
Was that funny?

33:29.100 --> 33:30.030
Cut it out.

33:41.350 --> 33:42.520
Oh my god.

33:43.540 --> 33:44.160
Jie.

33:46.330 --> 33:47.610
I'm done, Tang Jie.

33:47.630 --> 33:48.850
I was long done.

33:48.880 --> 33:49.610
Yan.

33:49.640 --> 33:50.820
You're on your own.

33:56.780 --> 33:58.340
Yan, go for it.

33:58.460 --> 33:59.390
Go for it.

34:14.330 --> 34:15.659
Your running posture's wrong,

34:15.690 --> 34:16.800
so it's more tiring.

34:17.030 --> 34:18.300
Swing your arms up,

34:18.730 --> 34:19.639
forward and back.

34:19.900 --> 34:21.340
Keep breathing.

34:22.790 --> 34:24.530
Lift up your calves with your thighs.

34:25.389 --> 34:26.030
Good.

34:27.150 --> 34:27.860
Come on.

34:28.020 --> 34:29.370
Lean forward a bit.

34:29.840 --> 34:30.830
Come, run with me.

34:34.989 --> 34:35.659
Keep up.

34:38.429 --> 34:39.550
What do we have there?

34:41.090 --> 34:43.100
Jiang Chengyi's running with Yan!

34:41.610 --> 34:44.280
♫When we're hand in hand, even the equator possesses♫

34:45.150 --> 34:48.139
♫Beauty like the aurora and white snow♫

34:49.520 --> 34:51.909
♫You close your eyes and make a wish, completely defenseless♫

34:52.530 --> 34:55.489
♫I kiss your face secretly♫

34:54.469 --> 34:55.370
How is it?

34:56.860 --> 34:59.610
♫I want to weave a beautiful dream for you♫

35:00.440 --> 35:02.730
♫What we lack is not just time♫

35:04.540 --> 35:07.070
♫Losing sight of the world and our default end point♫

35:07.750 --> 35:10.310
♫As we write every page of our love by hand♫

35:11.020 --> 35:13.020
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫
